tpp was written by Andreas Krennmair <ak@synflood.at> and Nico Golde <nico@ngolde.de>:
http://www.ngolde.de/tpp.html

And I simply make it a gem for super easy install:
sudo gem install tpp

Usage example::
tpp /Library/Ruby/Gems/1.8/gems/tpp-1.3.1/examples/list.tpp
tpp /Library/Ruby/Gems/1.8/gems/tpp-1.3.1/examples/source.tpp

There are more in the examples folde.
